Bayern Munich doctor Hans-Wilhelm Muller-Wohlfahrt quit this week after a reported rift with Pep Guardiola  . 
  The pair fell out over an injury to Philipp Lahm in training in November last year . 
  Guardiola complained that there was not a qualified doctor at the training ground . 
